{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01RQfeRexBxJgknGcqx7DxBk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error is because adding an arbiter with 2 data-bearing members would change the implicit default write concern. MongoDB by default uses `{w: \"majority\"}` as the default write concern when adding an arbiter to a PSA (Primary-Secondary-Arbiter) set. With PSA topology, the majority is 2 out of 3, but if the secondary goes down, writes would block.\n\nThe fix is to first set `defaultRWConcern` to `{w: 1}` or explicitly configure it before reconfiguring. The MongoDB documentation says to use `setDefaultRWConcern` command to set a cluster-wide write concern.\nI'll set the default write concern to `{w: 1}` before adding the arbiter to avoid this blocking issue.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":526,"cache_read_input_tokens":32573,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":526},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4eccdabb-15c2-4c15-897e-2873e96d6c8e","uuid":"6000eeb8-fc7f-402e-ab5b-86f58b064295","request_id":"req_011CcPoBGTrNWsKLF7QgupHX"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01RQfeRexBxJgknGcqx7DxBk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MongoDB requires setting a default write concern before adding an arbiter to a PSA topology. I'll set it first, then add the arbiter."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":526,"cache_read_input_tokens":32573,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":526},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4eccdabb-15c2-4c15-897e-2873e96d6c8e","uuid":"1f5e5f8b-a682-46be-9676-daade07a832d","request_id":"req_011CcPoBGTrNWsKLF7QgupHX"}
